# voice_assist

`voice_assist` is a Python module for hotword detection and speech-to-text functionality. It uses Picovoice Porcupine for hotword detection and Selenium for speech-to-text transcription.

## Features

- Hotword detection using Picovoice Porcupine.
- Speech-to-text transcription using a web-based service.
- Simple integration with text-to-speech services.

## Installation

You can install the module using pip:

```bash
pip install voice_assist
